    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a collector-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This specimen is in concours-level condition, with the valvetrain and double-VANOS system operating in perfect harmony. The mechanical integrity is superlative, featuring documented preventative maintenance on rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014essential for the S65's longevity. Power is delivered through a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical precision through corners. The chassis is taut, benefiting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and zero structural fatigue. Every bushing, seal, and fluid line reflects a vehicle maintained with an open checkbook. This is a visceral, high-RPM machine for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
