      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously garaged and cared for by a single owner, reflecting a level of preservation rarely seen on the market. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather retains its original matte finish and factory scent, with absolutely no bolster wear or fading on the high-traffic touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach\u2014every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership, and I have a comprehensive binder of every receipt and inspection report since new. It starts instantly, idles perfectly, and delivers a driving experience as tight and responsive as the day it left the assembly line. No leaks, no warning lights, and no stories\u2014just an investment-grade example for the discerning collector who demands the best.",
